xpertise helps make my job much easier.\r\nDecember 7, 2012,\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a><img alt="Picture" src="http://www.xstreaminspections.com/uploads/2/4/5/7/24575490/882202.jpg" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=2869808&amp;authToken=GQQZ">Alan Shaffer</a>Realtor, Clay Stapp + Co TheCondoGuy.com I\'ve worked with Shelly for several years now. She always helps my clients understand complex issues relating to home inspections and can explain what it means without scaring them to death and proving common sense answers and fixes for items found at the home.\r\nDecember 7, 2012,\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a><img alt="Picture" src="http://www.xstreaminspections.com/uploads/2/4/5/7/24575490/587843.jpg" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=14660328&amp;authToken=X_Tb">Cheryl O\'Hagan</a>Independent Real Estate Professional Shelly has inspected many properties for my buyers. She is timely, relates to the client, is always available for questions, even after the client moves in, has excellent people skills and her expert knowlegdeability of property is over the top. She is my #1 Inspector.\r\nNovember 29, 2012,\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a><img alt="Picture" src="http://www.xstreaminspections.com/uploads/2/4/5/7/24575490/4964356.jpg" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=13877239&amp;authToken=LEcF">Bruce Rayburn</a>Ebby Halliday REALTORS Shelly takes the time to show and explain potential issues to my clients. She is very patient with my first time home buyers and has a wide range of knowledge on many subjects.\r\nNovember 29, 2012,\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a><img alt="Picture" src="http://www.xstreaminspections.com/uploads/2/4/5/7/24575490/7428277.jpg" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=333767&amp;authToken=3t6c">Dennis O\'Hagan</a>Real Estate Agent at 