ww.xstreaminspections.com/uploads/2/4/5/7/24575490/3824841.jpg" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=6577704&amp;authToken=gokh">Rik Massengale</a>Commercial Real Estate I have used Shelly to inspect many homes and she is always on time and does an excellent job. She is thorough and identifies all issues that are important to be repaired before my buyer purchases the home. Shelly is great at explaining problem areas of a home to a buyer without scaring them and making them afraid to buy the home. I will be using Shelly many times in the..\r\nNovember 29, 2012,\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a><img alt="Picture" src="http://www.xstreaminspections.com/uploads/2/4/5/7/24575490/3696319.jpg" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=92590979&amp;authToken=vvFu">Ray Hooper</a>Executive Director of India Discipleship Network Shelly serves as a volunteer professional in our first-time homebuyers class teaching future homebuyers the importance of an inspection when buying a home. She is always well received and represents herself and her profession very well. She shows concern and interest in the client while demonstrating a high level of expertise in inspecting residential properties.\r\nNovember 21, 2012,\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a><img alt="Picture" src="http://www.xstreaminspections.com/uploads/2/4/5/7/24575490/1097913.jpg" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=68659557&amp;authToken=u3VB">Desiree Migon</a>Consultant Shelly is one of the best home inspectors in Dallas, with her detail, and understanding of home inspections, she can provide you the information you need ~\r\nMarch 18, 2013,\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a><img alt="Picture" src="http://www.xstreaminspections.com/uploads/2/4/5/7/24575490/6133288.jpg" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=172376092&amp;authToken=X4VN">HUNT HOLDRIDGE</a>Owner at HUNTAHOME, LLC Shelly is beyond amazing! You couldn\'t ask for a more detailed inspector to protect your interest. Her personable attitude and expert to details make her a valuable team player during the home buying process! Shelly thank you for all your hard work!!\r\nNovember 20, 2012,\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a><img alt="Picture" src="http://www.xstreaminspections.com/uploads/2/4/5/7/24575490/5765571.jpg" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=3014423&amp;authToken=-hQl">Eve Holder</a>D Mag\'s "Dallas\' Best Realtor" \'08-\'13 ~ KW Realty Luxury Home Marketing Expert Having worked in the Real Estate Industry for over 17 years, I feel my experience qualifies me to say "I know a great inspector when I see one!". And when it comes to "Great Inspectors", Shelly is at the top of the list! It goes beyond the fact that she is thorough or that she knows what she is doing. Her experience in homes of all ages has created in her, a professional.\r\nNovember 19, 2012,\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a><img alt="Picture" src="http://www.xstreaminspections.com/uploads/2/4/5/7/24575490/613465.jpg" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=27997092&amp;authToken=ibfL">Donna Parker</a>Real Estate Agent at Refined Realty Shelly brings the proper amount of expertise, years of experience, and calm to anyone thinking of purchasing a home, or doing a pre-listing report.\r\nOctober 9, 2012,\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a><img alt="Picture" src="http://www.xstreaminspections.com/uploads/2/4/5/7/24575490/36820.jpg" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=3014423&amp;authToken=-hQl">Eve Holder</a>D Mag\'s "Dallas\' Best Realtor" \'08-\'13 ~ KW Realty Luxury Home Marketing Expert With over 17 years in the real estate industry, I have used many inspectors over the years. But without a doubt, Shelly is one of the best I have worked with. She is thorough and professional and I can always trust the advise that Shelly gives my buyers and sellers. You can\'t go wrong in hiring Shelly to do your inspections.\r\nJune 20, 2012,\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a><img alt="Picture" src="http://www.xstreaminspections.com/uploads/2/4/5/7/24575490/45776.jpg" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=9434435&amp;authToken=8IDq">Adam Driver</a>Realtor at ReMax I am proud to count Shelly as a valuable asset to my real estate business. I have recommended her for the past 5 years to my clients and have always had outstanding results. Her knowledge of home inspection is the best I have ever seen. She has an outstanding personality and creates an atmosphere of teamwork with my clients to give them the best possible information and.\r\nJanuary 24, 2011,\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a><img alt="Picture" src="http://www.xstreaminspections.com/uploads/2/4/5/7/24575490/4223992.jpg" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=85323177&amp;authToken=BU_Q">Renee Roth</a>Center Director at Huntington Learning Center Shelly is a fantastic inspector! She really cares about helping each client to learn as much as possible about the house they will be buying. She points out things that are the most important problems as well as positives about the house they are buying,so they can proceed confidently with their purchase. I wholeheartedly recommend Shelly Morgan!\r\nJanuary 23, 2011,\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a><img alt="Picture" src="http://www.xstreaminspections.com/uploads/2/4/5/7/24575490/9530126.jpg" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=24318770&amp;authToken=MTW4">Mal Smith</a>Managing Broker at RE/MAX DFW Associates Shelly,\r\nIs highly recommended for residential real estate Inspections.\r\nHer knowledge of systems and her natural demeanor helps my clients feel comfortable with the home buying process. She is punctional, efficient and professional.\r\n\r\nMal SmithRE/MAX premier Group\r\nFRISCO, TX\r\nJanuary 23, 2011,\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a><img alt="Picture" src="http://www.xstreaminspections.com/uploads/2/4/5/7/24575490/3812103.jpg" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=35080963&amp;authToken=cVKC">Gary Grubbs</a>Account Executive at Oracle Shelly is an outstanding inspector that I highly recommend. I have hired Shelly to inspect homes on numerous occasions and have always found her to be very professional, knowledgeable, and an overall pleasure to work with. Whether you are a potential home buyer for investment or to live in, Shelly will represent you fairly and give you an objective assessment of the home.\r\nJanuary 23, 2011,\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a><img alt="Picture" src="http://www.xstreaminspections.com/uploads/2/4/5/7/24575490/5835706.jpg" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=19122997&amp;authToken=r_Zd">Brenda Washington</a>Realtor at Keller Williams Realty Plano Shelly has exceeded all my expectations; she is through, detailed, shows a great deal of integrity, and continually works on behalf of the buyer. Her interpersonal and communication skills are of the highest caliber and she will be recommended by me to my fellow associates and for my own clients. I consider her a valued member of my team in helping to make for seamless...\r\nApril 1, 2009,\r\n\r\n</div>', ' Testimonials', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-02-25 10:37:42', '2014-02-25 16:37:42', '', 14, 'http://xstreaminspections.com/14-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
