(187, 1, '2014-03-20 15:44:08', '2014-03-20 21:44:08', '<h1>Residential Inspections</h1>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>Types of Inspections</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Buyers Inspections</li>\r\n	<li>Existing Homes  Maintenance Inspections</li>\r\n	<li>Pre-Listing Inspections</li>\r\n	<li>New Home Inspections</li>\r\n	<li>Annual Home Maintenance Plans</li>\r\n	<li>One Year Warranty Inspections</li>\r\n	<li>Commercial Lease Space Inspections</li>\r\n	<li>Stand-Alone Buildings</li>\r\n	<li>Church Buildings</li>\r\n	<li>Television Studios</li>\r\n	<li>Daycares</li>\r\n	<li>Gas Stations</li>\r\n	<li>Private Schools/Daycares</li>\r\n	<li>High Rise Buildings</li>\r\n	<li>Apartment Complexes</li>\r\n	<li>Car Washes</li>\r\n	<li>Office Condos</li>\r\n	<li>Specialty Plumbing Tests/Inspections</li>\r\n	<li>Specialty Heating/Cooling Tests/Inspections</li>\r\n	<li>Specialty Electrical Tests/Inspections</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Items We Inspect</h2>\r\n<h3>Structural and Mechanical Inspections includes:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Foundation</li>\r\n	<li>Grading</li>\r\n	<li>Drainage</li>\r\n	<li>Doors</li>\r\n	<li>Windows</li>\r\n	<li>Interior and Exterior Walls</li>\r\n	<li>Roof Cover &amp; Roof Structure</li>\r\n	<li>Attic Ventilation &amp; Insulation</li>\r\n	<li>Electrical Panels &amp; Branch Circuits</li>\r\n	<li>Plumbing Systems &amp; Supply locations</li>\r\n	<li>Appliances</li>\r\n	<li>Heating Systems</li>\r\n	<li>Cooling Systems</li>\r\n	<li>Air Ducts</li>\r\n	<li>Floors and Ceilings</li>\r\n	<li>Garage</li>\r\n	<li>Garage Door Openers</li>\r\n	<li>Driveway</li>\r\n	<li>Porch Areas</li>\r\n	<li>Retaining Walls (if supporting foundation)</li>\r\n	<li>Stairways</li>\r\n	<li>Sprinklers</li>\r\n	<li>Gas Lines</li>\r\n	<li>Pools (additional fee)</li>\r\n	<li>Guest Quarters (additional fee)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>Note: Fences are not inspected</em>\r\n<h3>Wood Destroying Insect Inspection includes:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Foundation</li>\r\n	<li>Interior Walls and Cabinets</li>\r\n	<li>Attic Area</li>\r\n	<li>