(338, 1, '2014-03-24 23:05:17', '2014-03-25 05:05:17', '<h1>Testimonials</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=333767&amp;authToken=3t6c"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-306" alt="Denis O\'Hagan" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/1-3dae632-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a>\r\n<h2><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=333767&amp;authToken=3t6c">Dennis O\'Hagan</a></h2>\r\nReal Estate Agent at RE/MAX DFW Associates, International Real Estate Agent, RE/MAX Hall of Fame (Real Estate Services)\r\n\r\nShelley does an OUTSTANDING job as a Home Inspector. I have recommended her services to many clients and they have all been satisfied. I can highly recommend her services...\r\n\r\n<em>March 10, 2014</em>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=36954153&amp;authToken=7Z2s"><img class="alignnone  wp-image-307" alt="JoAnne Dzan Dozzi" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/2-34c461e.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a>\r\n<h2><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=36954153&amp;authToken=7Z2s">JoAnne Dzan Dozzi</a></h2>\r\nRealtor at RE/MAX Dallas Suburbs\r\n\r\nShelly is the most knowledgeable and professional inspector with whom I have worked. My favorite and her best asset is he unparalleled talent to speak with clients, delivering the pros and cons of a home in terms easily understood. The biggest differentiator: she tells it exactly as it is and at the same time does not unnecessarily scare them! This is an especially critical asset when speaking with first-time buyers. Someone should clone her! With her new company, she\'s gonna need two of her to handle all the work that will come her way!<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/profile/edit?trk=nav_responsive_sub_nav_edit_profile">\r\n</a>\r\n\r\n<em>March 10, 2014</em>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=141838408&amp;authToken=n9iR&amp;goback=%2Enpv_37197506_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_nav*4responsive*4tab*4profile*4pic_*1"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-308" alt="Carolyn Laun" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/3-0463655-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a>\r\n<h2><a title="" href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=141838408&amp;authToken=n9iR&amp;goback=%2Enpv_37197506_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_nav*4responsive*4tab*4profile*4pic_*1">Carolyn Laun</a></h2>\r\nIndependent Real Estate Professional\r\n\r\nShelly is honest &amp; thorough &amp; extremely knowledgeable. She communicates very well with the buyer, making sure they understand the issues, if any, with the property they are hoping to purchase, yet does not "scare them to death" if it isn\'t warranted.\r\n\r\n<em>July 27, 2013</em>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=16369065&amp;authToken=34wu&amp;goback=%2Enpv_37197506_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_nav*4responsive*4tab*4profile*4pic_*1"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-309" alt="Steve Goff" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/4-3ca416f-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><a title="" href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=16369065&amp;authToken=34wu&amp;goback=%2Enpv_37197506_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_nav*4responsive*4tab*4profile*4pic_*1">Steve Goff</a></h2>\r\nBroker/Owner CEDA REALTY\r\n\r\nShelly is a wonderful home inspector, possessing the unique combination of integrity, expertise and a genuine interest in the well being of her clients. I highly recommend her.\r\n\r\n<em>January 9, 2013</em>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=200787105&amp;authToken=0l5W&amp;goback=%2Enpv_37197506_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_nav*4responsive*4tab*4profile*4pic_*1"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-310" alt="Mal Smith" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/5-228ea1e-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=200787105&amp;authToken=0l5W&amp;goback=%2Enpv_37197506_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_nav*4responsive*4tab*4profile*4pic_*1">Mal Smith</a></h2>\r\nSales Manager at RE/MAX DFW Associates\r\n\r\nShelly is honest, straight forward, has great "bedside manner" with my clients being fair and objective, but not scaring them. Her professionalism is a credit to our industry. I will continue using her skills whenever my clients select her from my short list of most qualified inspectors in the DFW area.\r\n\r\n<em>January 2, 2013</em>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=11677695&amp;authToken=ca7B&amp;goback=%2Enpv_37197506_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_nav*4responsive*4tab*4profile*4pic_*1"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-311" alt="Corey Martin" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/6-17e0fe5-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=11677695&amp;authToken=ca7B&amp;goback=%2Enpv_37197506_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_nav*4responsive*4tab*4profile*4pic_*1">Corey Martin</a></h2>\r\nREALTOR/Property Manager\r\n\r\nI have enjoyed working with Shelly, my clients have been very happy with her professionalism and extensive knowledge makes Shelly my trusted source for anything Commerical/Residential inspection.\r\n\r\nThanks Shelly for all you do, looking forward to many more years of doing business together. Highly recommended\r\n\r\nCorey L. Martin, Realtor\r\nUltima Real Estate\r\n\r\n<em>December 10, 2012</em>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=30972590&amp;authToken=putQ&amp;goback=%2Enpv_37197506_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_nav*4responsive*4tab*4profile*4pic_*1"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-312" alt="Jerry Welch, GRI" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/7-21cb815-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=30972590&amp;authToken=putQ&amp;goback=%2Enpv_37197506_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_*1_nav*4responsive*4tab*4profile*4pic_*1">Jerry Welch, GRI</a></h2>\r\nREALTOR Consultant, International Real Estate Agent, Distressed Property Expert\r\n\r\nShelly is not just a home inspector, she is a valuable member of our real estate team. She is exceptional with clients and has a special way of helping them understand her reports, while at the same time pointing out any areas of concerns. And she does it without scaring them to death. Her expertise helps make my job much easier.\r\n\r\n<em>December 7, 2012</em>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=2869808&amp;authToken=GQQZ"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-313" alt="Alan Shaffer" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/8-0f2416d-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=2869808&amp;authToken=GQQZ">Alan Shaffer</a></h2>\r\nRealtor, Clay Stapp + Co TheCondoGuy.com\r\n\r\nI\'ve worked with Shelly for several years now. She always helps my clients understand complex issues relating to home inspections and can explain what it means without scaring them to death and proving common sense answers and fixes for items found at the home.\r\n\r\n<em>December 7, 2012</em>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=14660328&amp;authToken=X_Tb"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-314" alt="Cheryl O\'Hagan" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/9-1dc066e.jpg" width="101" height="101" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=14660328&amp;authToken=X_Tb">Cheryl O\'Hagan</a></h2>\r\nIndependent Real Estate Professional\r\n\r\nShelly has inspected many properties for my buyers. She is timely, relates to the client, is always available for questions, even after the client moves in, has excellent people skills and her expert knowlegdeability of property is over the top. She is my #1 Inspector.\r\n\r\n<em>November 29, 2012</em>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=13877239&amp;authToken=LEcF"><img class="alignnone  wp-image-315" alt="Bruce Rayburn" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/10-1f50db6.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=13877239&amp;authToken=LEcF">Bruce Rayburn</a></h2>\r\nEbby Halliday REALTORS\r\n\r\nShelly takes the time to show and explain potential issues to my clients. She is very patient with my first time home buyers and has a wide range of knowledge on many subjects.\r\n\r\n<em>November 29, 2012</em>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=333767&amp;authToken=3t6c"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-306" alt="Denis O\'Hagan" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/1-3dae632-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=333767&amp;authToken=3t6c">Dennis O\'Hagan</a></h2>\r\nReal Estate Agent at RE/MAX DFW Associates, International Real Estate Agent, RE/MAX Hall of Fame (Real Estate Services)\r\n\r\nShelly Morgan is "THE BEST" Home Inspector in the business... I have never had any issues come up after an Inspection which says a lot for how thorough she is with her job. She is tough but fair. She reviews every detail with the Buyer(s) and explains every problem/deficiency. Shelly clearly "knows her stuff" which is why she is always on the top of my "Home Inspector" list.\r\n\r\n<em>November 29, 2012</em>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=68659557&amp;authToken=u3VB"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-317" alt="Desiree Migon" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/12-3a7d35b-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=68659557&amp;authToken=u3VB">Desiree Migon</a></h2>\r\nConsultant\r\n\r\nCall Shelly Morgan for your next Commercial or Home Inspection, her expertise, quick response, understanding and knowledge of Inspections is remarkable and professional...\r\n\r\n<em>November 29, 2012</em>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=45700059&amp;authToken=H2L6"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-318" alt="Carole Rhodes" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/13-318e210-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=45700059&amp;authToken=H2L6">Carole Rhodes</a></h2>\r\nResidential Specialist at Briggs Freeman Sotheby\'s International Realty\r\n\r\nShelly is a very good &amp; professional inspector. She is thorough, but is not an alarmist. My Buyers have alway