50x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=3014423&amp;authToken=-hQl">Eve Holder</a></h2>\r\nD Magazine\'s "Dallas\' Best Realtor" 2008-2013 ~ KW Realty Luxury Home Marketing Expert\r\n\r\nHaving worked in the Real Estate Industry for over 17 years, I feel my experience qualifies me to say "I know a great inspector when I see one!". And when it comes to "Great Inspectors", Shelly is at the top of the list! It goes beyond the fact that she is thorough or that she knows what she is doing. Her experience in homes of all ages has created in her, a professional.\r\n\r\n<em> November 19, 2012</em>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=27997092&amp;authToken=ibfL"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-325" alt="Donna Parker" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/20-2b14469-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=27997092&amp;authToken=ibfL">Donna Parker</a></h2>\r\nReal Estate Agent at Refined Realty\r\n\r\nShelly brings the proper amount of expertise, years of experience, and calm to anyone thinking of purchasing a home, or doing a pre-listing report.\r\n\r\n<em>October 9, 2012</em>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=3014423&amp;authToken=-hQl"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-324" alt="Eve Holder" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/19-03b6137-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a></h1>\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=3014423&amp;authToken=-hQl">Eve Holder</a></h2>\r\nD Magazine\'s "Dallas\' Best Realtor" 2008-2013 ~ KW Realty Luxury Home Marketing Expert\r\n\r\nWith over 17 years in the real estate industry, I have used many inspectors over the years. But without a doubt, Shelly is one of the best I have worked with. She is thorough and professional and I can always trust the advise that Shelly gives my buyers and sellers. You can\'t go wrong in hiring Shelly to do your inspections.\r\n\r\n<em>June 20, 2012</em>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=9434435&amp;authToken=8IDq"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-327" alt="Adam Driver" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/22-090dfca-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a></h1>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=9434435&amp;authToken=8IDq">Adam Driver</a></h2>\r\nRealtor at ReMax\r\n\r\nI am proud to count Shelly as a valuable asset to my real estate business. I have recommended her for the past 5 years to my clients and have always had outstanding results. Her knowledge of home inspection is the best I have ever seen. She has an outstanding personality and creates an atmosphere of teamwork with my clients to give them the best possible information and.\r\n\r\n<em>January 24, 2011</em>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=85323177&amp;authToken=BU_Q"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-328" alt="Renee Roth" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/23-28117c8-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=85323177&amp;authToken=BU_Q">Renee Roth</a></h2>\r\nCenter Director at Huntington Learning Center\r\n\r\nShelly is a fantastic inspector! She really cares about helping each client to learn as much as possible about the house they will be buying. She points out things that are the most important problems as well as positives about the house they are buying,so they can proceed confidently with their purchase. I wholeheartedly recommend Shelly Morgan!\r\n\r\n<em>January 23, 2011</em>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=24318770&amp;authToken=MTW4"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-310" alt="Mal Smith" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/5-228ea1e-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=24318770&amp;authToken=MTW4">Mal Smith</a></h2>\r\nManaging Broker at RE/MAX DFW Associates\r\n\r\nShelly is highly recommended for residential real estate Inspections.\r\nHer knowledge of systems and her natural demeanor helps my clients feel comfortable with the home buying process. She is punctual, efficient and professional.\r\n\r\nMal SmithRE/MAX premier Group\r\nFRISCO, TX\r\n\r\n<em>January 23, 2011</em>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=35080963&amp;authToken=cVKC"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-330" alt="Gary Grubbs" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/25-2871b2f-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=35080963&amp;authToken=cVKC">Gary Grubbs</a></h2>\r\nAccount Executive at Oracle\r\n\r\nShelly is an outstanding inspector that I highly recommend. I have hired Shelly to inspect homes on numerous occasions and have always found her to be very professional, knowledgeable, and an overall pleasure to work with. Whether you are a potential home buyer for investment or to live in, Shelly will represent you fairly and give you an objective assessment of the home.\r\n\r\n<em>January 23, 2011</em>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h1><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=19122997&amp;authToken=r_Zd"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-331" alt="Brenda Washington" src="http://xstreaminspections.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/26-06880af-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" /></a></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=19122997&amp;authToken=r_Zd">Brenda Washington</a></h2>\r\nRealtor at Keller Williams Realty, Plano\r\n\r\nShelly has exceeded all my expectations; she is through, detailed, shows a great deal of integrity, and continually works on behalf of the buyer. Her interpersonal and communication skills are of the highest caliber and she will be recommended by me to my fellow associates and for my own clients. I consider her a valued member of my team in helping to make for seamless...\r\n\r\n<em>April 1, 2009</em>\r\n\r\n</div>', ' Testimonials', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-24 23:14:09', '2014-03-25 05:14:09', '', 14, 'http://xstreaminspections.com/14-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ;
